name: My Sàrmede Memoir 2017 (1)
description: There were 10 students in our class: me and Mango from Bangkok, Johanna Schmal from Germany, Nichole from Taiwan, Elena/Julia/Chiara/Rosanna and Claudia from Italy. Our wonderful teacher was Jesús Cineros from Mexico. He has learned Italian since March so he could communicated in Italian a little bit. He was very kind and tried to explain lesson step by step for me and Mango in English too.
